entries.journal_entry_description: The Jawas are happy that you saved them from the Tusken Raiders. You need to use that good feeling and find out what remainded of the smuggled cargo.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You saved the Jawas and got their encryption keys back. You need to talk with their Protocol Driod now to get the information on their sales of the cargo that they purchased.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You have gotten the Jawa Datapad
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You saved the Jawas. You need to talk with their Protocol Driod now to get the information on their sales of the cargo that they purchased.
entries.task03_message_box_text: You have gotten the last of the Jawa inventory. Time to get on with business.
